let _markdown = "\n\n## Quick Start Guide\n\nChr3D provides a unified Python ecosystem for analyzing 3D chromatin conformation data.\n\n### Hi-C Analysis\n\n```python\nfrom chr3d import HiC\n\nhic = HiC.from_cooler(\"data.cool\")\nhic_norm = hic.normalize(method=\"ICE\")\nloops = hic_norm.call_loops(method=\"hiccups\")\n```\n\n### ChIA-PET Analysis\n\n```python\nfrom chr3d import ChIAPET\n\nchiapet = ChIAPET.from_bedpe(\"interactions.bedpe\")\nfiltered = chiapet.filter_pets(min_pets=3)\npeaks = chiapet.call_peaks()\nloops = chiapet.call_loops(min_pets=3, peak_mode=True)\n```\n\n### HiChIP Analysis\n\n```python\nfrom chr3d import HiChIP\n\nhichip = HiChIP.from_pairs(\"pairs.txt\")\nloops = hichip.call_loops(method=\"hichipper\", fdr=0.01)\nhichip.to_cooler(\"output.cool\")\n```\n\n## Next Steps\n\n* [Complete Tutorials](../tutorials)\n* [API Reference](../api)\n* [Guides](../guides)\n";
